00:30:58.400 --> 00:30:59.680
What makes me happy.

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:07.360
When you do something just weigh it out,&nbsp;
will She be happy if we do like this.

00:31:08.080 --> 00:31:10.720
If we talk like this and say like these things.

00:31:10.720 --> 00:31:11.600
Will She be happy?

