Do not do what you want to do and you like it.

00:31:34.880 --> 00:31:35.920
That is a wrong style.

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:36.800
Absolutely wrong.

00:31:38.720 --> 00:31:41.680
But you must do what I would like you to do.

00:31:41.680 --> 00:31:45.840
And you know Me very well.

00:31:50.560 --> 00:31:54.480
And that is what it should be&nbsp;
that Mataji Prasanna(pleased).

